@startuml
title Client Query Builder (After)
skinparam backgroundColor #F7FAFC
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #2F3E46
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #B2EBF2
component "createTypedClient(...)" as TypedClient #C5E1A5
component "Registry\n(database->schema->model)" as Registry #FFF59D
component "Model Metadata\n(PK/nullability/relations)" as Metadata #FFE082
component "Tenant Context Mapper\n(configurable key map)" as Tenant #FFCCBC
component "Typed TableQueryBuilder<Row>" as TypedBuilder #D1C4E9
component "Identifier Quoting Layer" as Quoting #B3E5FC
component "Gateway Client" as Gateway #AED581
database "Athena HTTP Gateway" as GatewayApi #80CBC4

Consumer --> TypedClient : Configure URL + key + registry
TypedClient --> Registry : fromModel(db,schema,model)
Registry --> Metadata : Resolve row + table mapping
TypedClient --> Tenant : withTenantContext(...)
TypedClient --> TypedBuilder : Build typed chain
TypedBuilder --> Quoting : SQL fallback identifiers
Quoting --> Gateway : /gateway/query (quoted SQL)
TypedBuilder --> Gateway : /gateway/fetch|insert|update|delete
Gateway --> GatewayApi : HTTP request

note right of Quoting
Reserved names are auto-quoted
for generated SQL paths.
end note
@enduml
